experiment using a stationary muon, $\bar{v}_{\mathrm{e}}+\mathrm{v}_{\mu}$, carried away a total energy of $2.000 \times 10^{-12} \mathrm{~J}$, while the electron was moving with a kinetic energy of $1.4846 \times 10^{-11} \mathrm{~J}$. Determine the mass of the muon.
$$
\begin{aligned}
& E_{\mu}=m_{\mu} c^{2}=E_{\mathrm{e}}+E_{\mathrm{v}, \mathrm{v}} \\
